---
title: Carb Smart BBQ Pork Plate with Loaded Sweet Potatoes and Salad
description: Tonight, everyone's tried-and-true favourite BBQ plate gets the Carb Smart treatment! Pork chops are covered in smoky-sweet Southwest spices and BBQ sauce, while the classic loaded baked potato is revamped with sweet potato and caramelized onions.

Carb Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
